==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superaddition
<hw>Su`per*ad*di"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
adding something in excess or something extraneous; also, something
which is added in excess or extraneously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This <qex>superaddition</qex> is nothing but fat.</q>
<rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superadvenient</ent>⟦br⟧
